text: Phoutlamphay Thiamphasone (born September 9, 1979) is an archer from Laos. He competed at the 2004 Summer Olympics.Phoutlamphay ThiamphasonePhoutlamphay THIAMPHASONE == References == Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Laotian people Category:Archers Category:Olympians
